<div id="review_1792361047" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1792361047" />
    <a title="John Nelson" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/4924126-john-nelson"><img alt="John Nelson" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1486357423p2/4924126.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1792361047?book_show_action=true">Oct 23, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="John Nelson" class="user" itemprop="url" name="John Nelson" href="/user/show/4924126-john-nelson">John Nelson</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Hardcover 9780300044409" href="/book/show/3252414-civilization-before-greece-and-rome">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1792361047" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12925622973287775716">This book provides a very general overview of civilizations which existed in the ancient near East prior to the beginning of the Hellenic Age. Cultures covered include Egypt, Sumeria, Babylonia, Assyria, Phoenicia, Israel, Minoan Crete, and others. As is common with books that attempt to survey a very broad topic, this volume is able to provide only the most general discussion of the vast number of topics it addresses.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

