 learn after downloading this Spanish For Beginners book:   Introduction  Chapter 1: Learning Strategies Chapter 2: The Fundamentals Of Spanish Chapter 3: Numbers, Colors, Time, And Date Chapter 4: Nouns And Articles Chapter 5: Pronouns Chapter 6: Verbs Chapter 7: Adjectives Chapter 8: Prepositions, Adverbs, And Conjunctions Chapter 9: Forming Sentences Chapter 10: The Subjunctive &amp; Imperative Mood Chapter 11: Making Comparisons Chapter 12: Conversational Phrases and much more!   Get Your Copy Now!  <\/span>\n  <a data-text-id=\"5636647514962114212\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"swapContent(\$(this));; return false;\">...more<\/a>\n\n    <\/div>\n\n      <div class=\'wtrButtonContainer wtrSignedOut\' id=\'9_book_34604789\'>\n<div class=\'wtrUp wtrLeft\'>\n<form action=\"/shelf/add_to_shelf\" accept-charset=\"UTF-8\" method=\"post\"><input name=\"utf8\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"&#x2713;\" /><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"authenticity_token\" value=\"oQ7H+uACn2XdFNYR/S9+rj15vV8HsyQ7zwRTRYOkLjOMPsHwFzjhk9eaeA4B+ZP2WTJ/yQDuIxY8fisZuPHapg==\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_id\" id=\"book_id\" value=\"34604789\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"name\" id=\"name\" value=\"to-read\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"unique_id\" id=\"unique_id\" value=\"9_book_34604789\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"wtr_new\" id=\"wtr_new\" value=\"true\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_choice\" id=\"from_choice\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"from_home_module\" id=\"from_home_module\" value=\"false\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"ref\" id=\"ref\" value=\"\" class=\"wtrLeftUpRef\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"existing_review\" id=\"existing_review\" value=\"false\" class=\"wtrExisting\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"book_origin\" id=\"book_origin\" value=\"related_works\" />\n<input type=\"hidden\" name=\"page_url\" id=\"page_url\" value=\"/book/show/1649163.Civilization_Before_Greece_and_Rome\" />\n<button class=\'wtrToRead\' type=\'submit\'>\